profile:
Since 1992, Trico Homes has built new single and multi-family homes, offering a diverse selection of starter, move-up and semi-estate homes in Calgary, Airdrie, Chestermere, Cochrane, DeWinton and Okotoks. Whether you're looking for a quick possession or something more personalized, Trico’s team of dedicated staff will ensure you’ll find the perfect house to call home.

At Trico, we start every single day with one goal in mind; to deliver incredible life-changing moments. We know Calgarians have choices when buying a home. That’s why we’ve built a company that builds so much more than quality houses.

In the many years since Trico built our first home, our city has grown and so has our love for it. Along the way, we’ve become one of Calgary’s top builders - building over 11,500 single and multi-family homes and earning a reputation for our design, craftsmanship and customer care. Trico has received numerous accolades, including a Platinum member status as one of Canada’s 50 Best Managed Companies, Canada’s Best Workplaces, Canada's Top Small & Medium Employers, and a CHBA Excellence in Housing award. We are also proud to be Western Canada’s first and only homebuilder to become a certified B Corporation.

We’re committed to our industry and our city. We want to make our mark. To become a legacy company. We do more than develop quality homes. We help develop the place we call home.

Trico Homes. The Heart of Homebuilding.®

profile:
Excel Homes is a forward-thinking, energetic company, committed to creating innovative and thoughtfully designed homes. Since building our first house in 1988 we’ve focused on the evolving needs of our homebuyers to provide unparalleled value.
 
Looking to minimize our environmental footprint, and find new ways to add value, we joined the Built Green® program in 2007.  To date we’ve built over 2,200 Built Green® homes, are the second largest registrant in Canada, and are the proud recipients of a Built Green® Champion Award.
 
With 25-years of experience, over 10,000 single-family homes built, and 50 builder awards for design excellence, Excel Homes is honoured to be one of greater Calgary’s leading builders.

profile:
Ours is a privately-owned and fully integrated Plan, Design & Build firm, highly specialized in residential & commercial development projects. At Artistique Homes, it is the focus of our business to provide individual attention to every client that covers every stage of the project and our business relationship.  
Each project at Artistique Homes begins with a belief that great, consumer-centered ideas and design can play a critical role in getting done our client’s project successfully.  We don’t believe in simply making things look pretty; we believe in creating consumer touchpoints that build relationships and effective communication strategies that drive project success. 
Over the last 20 years, has successfully built and managed projects into the Calgary real estate market, an achievement attributed to a well-managed organization with an unwavering belief in quality and treating our valued Clients the right way.

Artistique Homes distinguishes itself with the promise of superb craftsmanship and design. With the strong belief in Quality, Integrity and Commitment the Firm has establishes the reputation of being one of the most respected Builders and Developer of Alberta

profile:
As the premier custom home builder and luxury renovation experts of the Calgary area, we put our 20+ years of experience to work for you. 

Your Green Cedar Home is more than just a place to live. It’s a perfectly crafted space for living, your way. 

Whether you want to linger on architectural details or spend more time with the interior designer, you’ll get the attention you need to truly customize your lifestyle ecosystem.

To us, building custom homes is more than blueprints and tweaks to floorplans. We manage the process, protect your vision, and add value at every step. 

From concept to creation, our velvet rope experience will usher you through the building process, into living your dream in your dream home.
